en_5464296_0	The Ministry of Public Administration, Provincial Councils and Local Government has decided to implement a new wage structure for public sector employees.
en_5464296_1	Ministry Secretary J. Dadallage, stated that the new salary structure will be implemented in collaboration with the Ministry of Finance. Discrepancies have arisen among government employees due to the occasional salary increments and circulars that have been issued. The Secretary to the Ministry stated that they are planning on eliminating these discrepancies with the new salary structure.
en_5464296_2	He further stated that  in line with the salary growth , through this method regulations for public servants will also be brought about.This process is scheduled to be completed before the end of next month where ideas will be tabled by trade unions.
